# PyCharm HTTP Client requests
# 使用方法：在 PyCharm 右上角选择环境 dev（来自 http-client.env.json），然后逐个发送请求。
# 认证：当前后端未强制校验，可保留现有 Token 头；后续接入 JWT 时推荐使用：
# Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
# 下面示例仍使用 Token: {{token}} 以保持一致。

### User - Register
POST {{base_url}}/user/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "tom",
  "phone": "13800000001",
  "email": "tom@example.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!",
  "birthday": "1990-01-01",
  "avatar_url": "/static/user_avatar_images/01.png"
}

### User - Login (sets global token)
POST {{base_url}}/user/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13733715212",
  "password": "200249"
}

> {%
  const body = JSON.parse(response.body || '{}');
  const token = body?.data?.token || body?.token;
  if (token) {
    client.global.set("token", token);
  }
%}

### User - Login (fail wrong password)
POST {{base_url}}/user/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13733715212",
  "password": "WRONG_PASS"
}

### User - Logout
POST {{base_url}}/user/logout/
Token: {{token}}

### User - Me (by username)
GET {{base_url}}/user/me/?username=tom
Token: {{token}}

### User - Me (missing param error)
GET {{base_url}}/user/me/
Token: {{token}}

